// carries it. app.js lazy-loads this module (ensureTools) only when it
// needs to route a tile hash, render a tool view, or power search --
// never at home first paint. The build / lint scripts that enumerate
// the catalog read the TOOLS array from THIS file, not app.js.
//
// The `{ id, name, group, trades, desc }` row shape and the inline
// `// Group X:` section comments are preserved verbatim so the regex
// parsers and the per-group comment splits keep matching.

